   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "from scipy.stats import norm\n",
    "from scipy.stats import binom\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 1a)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### Delta"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def bsmCallDelta(spot, strike, vol, rate, tau, div):\n",
    "    D1= (np.log(spot / strike) + (rate - div + 0.5 * vol * vol) * tau) / (vol * np.sqrt(tau))\n",
    "    Delta= np.exp(-div * tau) * norm.cdf(d1)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return Delta"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def bsmPutDelta(spot, strike, vol, rate, tau, div):\n",
    "    d1= (np.log(spot / strike) + (rate - div + 0.5 * vol * vol) * tau) / (vol * np.sqrt(tau))\n",
    "    Delta= np.exp(-div * tau) * norm.cdf(-d1)\n",
    "\n",
    "    return Delta"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### Gamma"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def bsmCallGamma(spot, strike, vol, rate, tau, div):\n",
    "    d1= (np.log(spot / strike) + (rate - div + 0.5 * vol * vol) * tau) / (vol * np.sqrt(tau))\n",
    "    gamma= (np.exp(-div * tau) * norm.pdf(d1))/(spot * vol * np.sqrt(tau))\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return gamma"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def bsmPutGamma(spot, strike, vol, rate, tau, div):\n",
    "    d1= (np.log(spot / strike) + (rate - div + 0.5 * vol * vol) * tau) / (vol * np.sqrt(tau))\n",
    "    gamma= (np.exp(-div * tau) * norm.pdf(d1))/(spot * vol * np.sqrt(tau))\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return gamma"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### Rho"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def bsmCallRho(spot, strike, vol, rate, tau, div):\n",
    "    d1= (np.log(spot / strike) + (rate - div + 0.5 * vol * vol) * tau) / (vol * np.sqrt(tau))\n",
    "    d2= d1 - (vol * np.sqrt(tau))\n",
    "    Rho=  tau * strike * (np.exp(-rate * tau)) * norm.cdf(d2)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return Rho"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def bsmPutRho(spot, strike, vol, rate, tau, div):\n",
    "    d1= (np.log(spot / strike) + (rate - div + 0.5 * vol * vol) * tau) / (vol * np.sqrt(tau))\n",
    "    d2= d1 - (vol * np.sqrt(tau))\n",
    "    Rho=  -tau * strike * (np.exp(-rate * tau)) * norm.cdf(-d2)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return Rho"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### Theta"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def bsmCallTheta(spot, strike, vol, rate, tau, div):\n",
    "    d1= (np.log(spot / strike) + (rate - div + 0.5 * vol * vol) * tau) / (vol * np.sqrt(tau))\n",
    "    d2= d1 - (vol * np.sqrt(tau))\n",
    "    theta= (div * strike ** (-div * tau) * norm.cdf(d1)) - (rate * strike * np.exp(-rate * tau) * norm.cdf(d2))\n",
    "    - ((strike * np.exp(-rate * tau * norm.pdf(d2) * vol))/2 * np.sqrt(tau))\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return theta"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def bsmPutTheta(spot, strike, vol, rate, tau, div):\n",
    "    d1= (np.log(spot / strike) + (rate - div + 0.5 * vol * vol) * tau) / (vol * np.sqrt(tau))\n",
    "    d2= d1 - (vol * np.sqrt(tau))\n",
    "    theta= ((div * strike ** (-div * tau) * norm.cdf(d1)) - (rate * strike * np.exp(-rate * tau) * norm.cdf(d2))\n",
    "    - ((strike * np.exp(-rate * tau * norm.pdf(d2) * vol))/2 * np.sqrt(tau)))\n",
    "    + ((rate * strike * np.exp(-rate * tau)) - (div * spot * np.exp(-div * tau)))\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return theta"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### Vega"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def bsmCallVega(spot, strike, vol, rate, tau, div):\n",
    "    d1= (np.log(spot / strike) + (rate - div + 0.5 * vol * vol) * tau) / (vol * np.sqrt(tau))\n",
    "    vega= (spot * np.exp(-div * tau)) * norm.pdf(d1) * np.sqrt(tau)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return vega"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 11,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def bsmPutVega(spot, strike, vol, rate, tau, div):\n",
    "    d1= (np.log(spot / strike) + (rate - div + 0.5 * vol * vol) * tau) / (vol * np.sqrt(tau))\n",
    "    vega= (spot * np.exp(-div * tau)) * norm.pdf(d1) * np.sqrt(tau)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return vega"
   ]
  },

    "def plotPricePath(path):\n",
    "    nsteps = path.shape[0]\n",
    "    plt.plot(path, 'b', linewidth = 2.5)\n",
    "    plt.title(\"Simulated Daily Prices\")\n",
    "    plt.xlabel(\"Time Steps\")\n",
    "    plt.ylabel(\"Stock Price ($)\")\n",
    "    plt.xlim((0, nsteps - 1))\n",
    "    plt.grid(True)\n",
    "    plt.show()"
   ]

    "S = 41.0\n",
    "K = 40.0\n",
    "v = 0.30\n",
    "r = 0.08\n",
    "q = 0.0\n",
    "T = 1.0\n",
    "n = 6\n",
    "h = T / 252\n",
    "\n",
    "path = np.zeros(n)\n",
    "z = np.random.normal(size=n)\n",
    "path[0] = S\n",
    "\n",
    "for t in range(1, n):\n",
    "    path[t] = path[t-1] * np.exp((r - q - 0.5 * v * v) * h + v * np.sqrt(h) * z[t])\n",
    "    \n",
    "plotPricePath(path)"
